MysteryCandy: {
	DisplayName: Mystery Candy
	Tooltip: Either a great treat... or a nasty trick

	Positive: {
		1: Sweet and filling. You feel restored.
		2: The sugar rush hits hard.
		3: Mmm, the fluffiest of nougats. You feel light as a feather.
		4: Magic is sparking from your fingertips. Maybe the candy was enchanted after all.
		5: Has a bit of a metallic taste, but your skin is now tough as titanium.
		6: It's a great time to go exploring.
		7: You can see all.
		8: Your hands are perfectly steady now.
		9: That was delicious.
		10: The conditions are perfect for a bit of building.
		11: Your wish is their command.
		12: New strength surges through your body.
		13: The ground drops beneath your feet.
		14: You feel like you're gonna make a big catch.
	}

	Negative: {
		Hurt: "{0} bit on a razorblade."
		1: Ouch, there was a razorblade in there!
		2: Your legs can barely hold you.
		3: You are encased in stone.
		4: Every last spark of magic left your body. Maybe the candy was enchanted after all.
		5: Your armor is crumpling at the slightest touch.
		6: You can barely think straight.
		7: You are frozen in place. Maybe mint was a bad idea...
		8: You can't feel your arms.
		9: Your limbs ache with the slightest movement.
		10: You've been drugged.
		11: You feel sick.
	}
}

